I Wouldn’t Trade My Life With None Of Y’all - It’s An Embargo.

💥 #8monthspregnant 💥

Ready When You Are….💙🫶🏾 #8Months 

You have the best example for a dad to love, support, guide, groom & teach you how to be the perfect gentleman.

The best big sister to teach you the importance of self care, being a leader & how to have fun!

& a mom that’s going to protect & cherish you every second of the day 4Life!

🖤 My Life Is Complete 🖤 

 MY SON > KHROME VANROSS! 
#BabyV - THANK GOD.

A Couple Titles To My Name But The One I Don’t Play About Is #MOTHER 💕 

So Shoutout To Me… For Never Givin’ Up On My Kids - For Always Being Present & Goin’ Hard & For Being Selfless When It Comes To Mine. I THANK GOD EVERY SECOND OF THE DAY, THESE KIDS HAVE MADE A WOMAN OF ME. #HappyMothersDay 🙏🏾🫶🏾

& #shoutout to @versatilevisionz & @ryansimsbeauty for getting us together last min. 😂🫶🏾💕

Happy Father’s Day hubby… we are blessed to have such a present , selfless & family focused man of the house. Love and appreciate all that you do - & although this is your 1st Father’s Day you have truly always been the most nurturing person I know & I Pray God blesses you to see 100 more Father’s Day! Hope you feel loved and appreciated today as you make us feel every second of every day… I LOVE YOUUUUU! 💕
Strongest Yet - The Softest I’ve Ever Been! #HappyBirthdayToMe ♋️

KHROME VANROSS THE 🌍 IS YOURS!  #6monthsold

🤍 RENAISSANCE WORLD TOUR 🤍

Reppin’ for the girls that’s takin over the world! We love you BEYONCE & Blue Ivy!

Thankful to have gone to see this amazing show - to see the Queen - with my daughter again, 6 years later. A time was hadddddd! We would go again & again & again had the tour not been coming to an end! BEYONCEEEEEEE…. OK GWROLLLLL! 👑🐝😂

#renaissance #houston #beyonce

RENAISSANCE WORLD TOUR. Houston, Tx - Night ✌🏾🤟🏾. Words can’t even describe how perfect the show was… THE QUEEN. BLUE IVY. THE DANCERS… THE PRODUCTION TEAM WORKED OVER TIMEEEEEE! THE FANS, THE FITS!!!!!! I WILL NEVER FORGET. 🐝🐝🐝🐝
FAIR DATE w/ my boys. 🎡⭐️🎟️ Now will Khrome get to go again… HMMM PROBABLY NOT. 😂😂😂
